reviews.text: We had a delicious meal at Spicy Island. Best curry and one of the best Indian restaurants in Hong Kong. Very friendly staff and wonderful atmosphere. Book a table though as this place gets very busy in evenings. Highly recommended !!

Hi bad service just expectation was a friendly service instead get accused  the owner should learn to train the staff how to do customer service not to be rude  and the owner defends a staff I am not a trouble. Maker  but these people really. Don’t know how to give good customer service I went to another resturant water front cafe and got good service I don’t have any bad motives just share my experience
I think the food was as good as on Sri Lanka itself though of course many times as costly.  Tried many dishes and was satisfied with everything.
Good value Indian restaurant on Lamma Island, with indoor and outdoor seating and friendly staff. Recommended.
Good food and beer and price are cheap, will come again and highly recommended 😋😋😋
